name: SIGIL OF THE SUN
description:
The burning force behind life on earth, like a watchful father over us the sun hangs like a giant idol in the sky. The most powerful celestial body in our galaxy, it burns and radiates energy enough to set the world aflame in a single moment.
Gaze into it's magnificent glory and remember: There is no shadow without light.
 
800x800gif made on a Deluxe Paint emulator for the MS-DOS
